Anytime my SO(28M) ejaculates in me(26F) I have a HORRIBLE burning sensation. I don't want to pee, I don't want to walk, I just have to lie there until it goes away (5-10 minutes). The feeling develops maybe 2 minutes after finishing intercourse.

I'm suspected to have endometriosis, haven't been tested by my gynecologist is going off of clinical signs. I just saw the gynecologist 2 weeks ago but forgot to mention the burning
